WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.210 --> 00:00:01.380
- [Narrator] If you're a small YouTuber

00:00:01.380 --> 00:00:03.840
and your videos are getting zero views,

00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:06.240
this two-minute hack
will change everything.

00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:08.160
I'm going to show you the hidden settings

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:10.800
that most creators don't even know exist.

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:12.300
Here's the brutal truth.

00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:13.500
When you're a new channel,

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:16.650
YouTube has no idea what
your content is about,

00:00:16.650 --> 00:00:19.980
or who should see it, so
your videos get buried.

00:00:19.980 --> 00:00:22.980
But YouTube actually
tells us how to fix this.

00:00:22.980 --> 00:00:26.730
According to YouTube, new
channels must rely on metadata.

00:00:26.730 --> 00:00:29.490
Your titles, descriptions,
and other signals

00:00:29.490 --> 00:00:32.400
to help the algorithm
understand your content.

00:00:32.400 --> 00:00:34.380
But there are three secret settings

00:00:34.380 --> 00:00:36.060
that most creators never touch,

00:00:36.060 --> 00:00:38.760
that literally teach the
algorithm who you are,

00:00:38.760 --> 00:00:40.200
who should see your videos,

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:43.350
and get YouTube to start
recommending your content

00:00:43.350 --> 00:00:44.520
to the right people.

00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:46.740
I'm about to walk you through each one.

00:00:46.740 --> 00:00:49.320
So let's start with the
first one. Channel keywords.

00:00:49.320 --> 00:00:50.986
These are invisible keywords

00:00:50.986 --> 00:00:53.310
that describe your entire channel,

00:00:53.310 --> 00:00:55.590
not just individual videos.

00:00:55.590 --> 00:00:56.490
Here's how.

00:00:56.490 --> 00:00:59.610
Click your profile photo,
go to YouTube Studio,

00:00:59.610 --> 00:01:02.880
then click Settings, then Channel.

00:01:02.880 --> 00:01:04.680
You'll see a keyword section

00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:07.860
that 99% of creators leave empty.

00:01:07.860 --> 00:01:10.920
Add broad keywords like fitness or finance

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:12.780
or whatever your channel is about,

00:01:12.780 --> 00:01:15.270
but also add long tail phrases

00:01:15.270 --> 00:01:17.640
your audience actually searches for.

00:01:17.640 --> 00:01:21.030
Instead of just fitness, add,
"how to lose weight fast,"

00:01:21.030 --> 00:01:23.670
or "home workout routines."

00:01:23.670 --> 00:01:26.160
As a regular viewer browsing YouTube,

00:01:26.160 --> 00:01:28.470
you can't actually see these keywords

00:01:28.470 --> 00:01:31.110
that channels are using
to help the algorithm

00:01:31.110 --> 00:01:33.420
push your content to the right viewers.

00:01:33.420 --> 00:01:35.880
But with a two buddy extension installed,

00:01:35.880 --> 00:01:38.760
you can spy on a channel's keywords.

00:01:38.760 --> 00:01:41.460
That means you can go look
at the biggest channels

00:01:41.460 --> 00:01:45.450
in your niche, see exactly
what keywords they're using,

00:01:45.450 --> 00:01:47.580
and model what's working for them.

00:01:47.580 --> 00:01:51.000
The second hack is in the
upload default settings.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:53.760
In that same menu, click Upload Defaults.

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:56.700
This is gold because
every video you upload

00:01:56.700 --> 00:02:00.630
will automatically include
these descriptions and tags.

00:02:00.630 --> 00:02:02.877
What I want you to do here
is write a description

00:02:02.877 --> 00:02:06.780
about your channel, what
it's about, who you help,

00:02:06.780 --> 00:02:08.160
what topics you cover.

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:11.010
If you need help, just look
at this video's description,

00:02:11.010 --> 00:02:13.710
but think about this
like your elevator pitch

00:02:13.710 --> 00:02:14.700
for your channel.

00:02:14.700 --> 00:02:17.700
Now, every time you upload a new video,

00:02:17.700 --> 00:02:21.870
YouTube will automatically
populate this entire description.

00:02:21.870 --> 00:02:24.930
And above it, you can just add
whatever custom description

00:02:24.930 --> 00:02:27.030
you have for that specific video.

00:02:27.030 --> 00:02:29.100
This saves a load of time,

00:02:29.100 --> 00:02:32.190
and make sure that each video
has detailed information

00:02:32.190 --> 00:02:34.770
in the description that
helps the algorithm

00:02:34.770 --> 00:02:37.350
push your video to the right viewers.

00:02:37.350 --> 00:02:41.190
Now, for the third and
final setting, default tags.

00:02:41.190 --> 00:02:43.500
This one is massive for new channels,

00:02:43.500 --> 00:02:45.570
because tags are one of the main things

00:02:45.570 --> 00:02:49.020
that YouTube relies on when
your channel is brand new,

00:02:49.020 --> 00:02:51.150
and the algorithm doesn't have enough data

00:02:51.150 --> 00:02:52.800
about your content yet.

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:56.250
You'll find this in the
same upload default section.

00:02:56.250 --> 00:02:59.400
What you want to do is
add about two to five tags

00:02:59.400 --> 00:03:01.650
that describe your channel as a whole.

00:03:01.650 --> 00:03:03.930
These tags will automatically be added

00:03:03.930 --> 00:03:06.540
to every single video you upload.

00:03:06.540 --> 00:03:09.930
No extra work, no remembering
to add them manually.

00:03:09.930 --> 00:03:11.220
Just like with keywords,

00:03:11.220 --> 00:03:13.652
you want to make sure you
use a mix of broad terms

00:03:13.652 --> 00:03:16.380
with long tail phrases.

00:03:16.380 --> 00:03:18.060
These three settings work together

00:03:18.060 --> 00:03:20.550
like a GPS for the algorithm.

00:03:20.550 --> 00:03:24.270
They tell YouTube exactly
where to drive your content,

00:03:24.270 --> 00:03:27.540
so your videos can get
recommended to more people.

00:03:27.540 --> 00:03:30.660
Now, getting recommended
is just the first step.

00:03:30.660 --> 00:03:32.850
If you're looking to get monetized,

00:03:32.850 --> 00:03:35.220
watch time is going to be critical.

00:03:35.220 --> 00:03:37.620
And if you want to hit that 4,000 hours

00:03:37.620 --> 00:03:40.050
of watch time milestone faster,

00:03:40.050 --> 00:03:43.083
I just made this video that
I want you to watch next.

